[0.011, "o", "\u001b[0;1;31m×\u001b[0m mariadb.service - MariaDB 12.3.2 database server\r\n     Loaded: loaded (\u001b]8;;file://khai/usr/lib/systemd/system/mariadb.service\u001b\\/usr/lib/systemd/system/mariadb.service\u001b]8;;\u001b\\; \u001b[0;1;32menabled\u001b[0m; preset: \u001b[0;1;38:5:185mdisabled\u001b[0m)\r\n    Drop-In: /usr/lib/systemd/system/mariadb.service.d\r\n             └─\u001b]8;;file://khai/usr/lib/systemd/system/mariadb.service.d/galera.conf\u001b\\galera.conf\u001b]8;;\u001b\\\r\n     Active: \u001b[0;1;31mfailed\u001b[0m (Result: exit-code) since Tue 2026-06-23 03:13:26 WIB; 19s ago\r\n Invocation: 8236876e2372434483609c882ba1c5f1\r\n       Docs: \u001b]8;;man:mariadbd(8)\u001b\\man:mariadbd(8)\u001b]8;;\u001b\\\r\n             \u001b]8;;https://mariadb.com/kb/en/library/systemd/\u001b\\https://mariadb.com/kb/en/library/systemd/\u001b]8;;\u001b\\\r\n    Process: 4004 ExecStartPre=/bin/sh -c [ ! -e /usr/bin/galera_recovery ] && VAR= ||   VAR=`/usr/bin/galera_recovery`; [ $? -eq 0 ]   && echo _WSREP_START_POSITION=$VAR > /run/mariadb/wsrep-start-position || exit 1 (code=exited, status=0/SUCCESS)\r\n    Process: 4030 ExecStart=/usr/bin/mariadbd $MYSQLD_OPTS $_WSREP_NEW_CLUSTER $_WSREP_START_POSITION \u001b[0;1;31m(code=exited, status=1/FAILURE)\u001b[0m\r\n   Main PID: 4030 (code=exited, status=1/FAILURE)\r\n     Status: \"\u001b[0;1;36mMariaDB server is down\u001b[0m\"\r\n   Mem peak: 94M\r\n        CPU: 445ms\r\n\r\nJun 23 03:13:26 khai mariadbd[4030]: 2026-06-23  3:13:26 0 [Note] InnoDB: Buffer pool(s) load completed at 260623  3:13:26\r\nJun 23 03:13:26 khai mariadbd[4030]: 2026-06-23  3:13:26 0 [Warning] Can't open and lock privilege tables: Table 'mysql.servers' doesn't exist\r\nJun 23 03:13:26 khai mariadbd[4030]: 2026-06-23  3:13:26 0 [Note] Server socket created on IP: '0.0.0.0', port: '3306'.\r\nJun 23 03:13:26 khai mariadbd[4030]: 2026-06-23  3:13:26 0 [Note] Server socket created on IP: '::', port: '3306'.\r\nJun 23 03:13:26 khai mariadbd[4030]: 2026-06-23  3:13:26 0 [ERROR] Fatal error: Can't open and lock privilege tables: Table 'mysql.db' doesn't exist\r\nJun 23 03:13:26 khai mariadbd[4030]: 2026-06-23  3:13:26 0 [ERROR] Aborting\r\nJun 23 03:13:26 khai systemd[1]: \u001b[0;1;39m\u001b[0;1;31m\u001b[0;1;39mmariadb.service: Main process exited, code=exited, status=1/FAILURE\u001b[0m\r\nJun 23 03:13:26 khai systemd[1]: \u001b[0;1;38:5:185m\u001b[0;1;39m\u001b[0;1;38:5:185mmariadb.service: Failed with result 'exit-code'.\u001b[0m\r\nJun 23 03:13:26 khai systemd[1]: \u001b[0;1;31m\u001b[0;1;39m\u001b[0;1;31mFailed to start MariaDB 12.3.2 database server.\u001b[0m\r\nJun 23 03:13:26 khai systemd[1]: mariadb.service: Consumed 445ms CPU time over 600ms wall clock time, 94M memory peak.\r\n"]
